Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(542,200)\fs60\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\move(960,760,960,800)\t(\fs72)}血 系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.66,EN,,0,0,0,,1476, the dawn of a new era for Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:17.96,EN,,0,0,0,,Arts, culture and science are flourishing under the guidance of inspired minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Renaissance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.26,EN,,0,0,0,,This is probably the way history will remember us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:45.06,EN,,0,0,0,,But in the shadows far from the gold, and the knowledge, lies another truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:50.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:51.58,EN,,0,0,0,,Betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.62,EN,,0,0,0,,Secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:59.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Secrets so dangerous I must hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:01.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Even from my own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Family, justice, honour,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.80,EN,,0,0,0,,These are the values guiding my blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:15.90,EN,,0,0,0,,This truth is written in blood and the shadows are where I strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.28,EN,,0,0,0,,I am Giovanne Auditore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.98,EN,,0,0,0,,And like my ancestors before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.16,EN,,0,0,0,,I am an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.56,EN,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me, Avanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.46,EN,,0,0,0,,I stopped them before Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, Your Magnificence, the fourth man escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.44,EN,,0,0,0,,What have you heard, Giovanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.06,EN,,0,0,0,,About an important event that will cause a shift of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.84,EN,,0,0,0,,That man you captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Has he spoken yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.72,EN,,0,0,0,,He will tell us what he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.56,EN,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Tell me when!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:20.98,EN,,0,0,0,,In Milano, on the day of Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:30.38,EN,,0,0,0,,The high mass called the priest of Santo Stefano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.35,EN,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:38.38,EN,,0,0,0,,When the echo of the choir becomes louder at the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:45.96,EN,,0,0,0,,When the bell rings for the twelfth and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:52.78,EN,,0,0,0,,At the altar, the echo of the choir becomes louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.50,EN,,0,0,0,,When the bell rings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:04.70,EN,,0,0,0,,For the twelfth and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.80,EN,,0,0,0,,The duke of Milano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.17,EN,,0,0,0,,Will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.46,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Amore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.88,EN,,0,0,0,,Ezio's learning fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.80,EN,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:37.09,EN,,0,0,0,,Ezio, remember, you need to think ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:42.80,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't wait for your opponent to move, anticipate and surprise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.48,EN,,0,0,0,,How are you, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.54,EN,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:04.18,EN,,0,0,0,,With the death of the Duke of Milano, Lorenzo de Medici has lost a powerful ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.44,EN,,0,0,0,,I am sure that his enemies already plot their next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Sforsa's death was not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.36,EN,,0,0,0,,It was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.04,EN,,0,0,0,,And I know where to fight my next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.76,EN,,0,0,0,,You served us well in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.06,EN,,0,0,0,,That is why we are entrusting you to send this letter to our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.72,EN,,0,0,0,,It's Perfect. It's just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.66,EN,,0,0,0,,After all these years, our time has come, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.58,EN,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:57.04,EN,,0,0,0,,You must protect this letter with your life until it is delivered, you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Go to Campus Sant Anzono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:09.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Next to the one merchant there's a statue. A man will be waiting for you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Do not fail us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.36,EN,,0,0,0,,What are your masters plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.76,EN,,0,0,0,,God is my witness, I will cut your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:51.20,EN,,0,0,0,,My life is not yours to take, and my secrets come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.78,EN,,0,0,0,,See you in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Giovanni, did you find anything in Venice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.96,EN,,0,0,0,,I intercepted this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.82,EN,,0,0,0,,Take a look, your Magnificence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.50,EN,,0,0,0,,It bears the seal of the Barbarigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.66,EN,,0,0,0,,I never trusted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Confidantiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.08,EN,,0,0,0,,An encrypted letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.46,EN,,0,0,0,,It will take several hours to unlock its secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.32,EN,,0,0,0,,I'll send for you when it's done, Giovanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.00,EN,,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.78,EN,,0,0,0,,Father Maffei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:36.58,EN,,0,0,0,,You broke the code. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.66,EN,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't disappoint me, Father Maffei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Go fetch Giovanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.56,EN,,0,0,0,,Tell him he would need to travel shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.66,EN,,0,0,0,,I will wait Lorenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.32,EN,,0,0,0,,And Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Remember, you owe us your silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Secrets are born here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.48,EN,,0,0,0,,And they die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.48,EN,,0,0,0,,No one is to know about the content of this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Capisci?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Good, you can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.66,EN,,0,0,0,,Come back to us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.32,EN,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Our son is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.36,EN,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.62,EN,,0,0,0,,You should talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.14,EN,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:17.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Tell me, papa, why is it that a banker has to leave so often in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.22,EN,,0,0,0,,Business calls, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Let me come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.27,EN,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.18,EN,,0,0,0,,I need you to assist your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Take care of the family while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.54,EN,,0,0,0,,I want to help you, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.66,EN,,0,0,0,,You help me more than you know, Ezio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.93,EN,,0,0,0,,More than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Because we broke the seal of the original letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.10,EN,,0,0,0,,We had to make an exact copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.12,EN,,0,0,0,,Father Edmundi is working on one as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.10,EN,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.60,EN,,0,0,0,,We were unable to decipher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:15.08,EN,,0,0,0,,The only way to unlock the secrets of this letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.96,EN,,0,0,0,,And find out who masterminded Sforza's assassination...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:22.64,EN,,0,0,0,,is to deliver it and see where it will lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:23.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Your Magnificence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:28.92,EN,,0,0,0,,I know exactly where in Rome the Barbargos wanted the letter to be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Father Maffei, is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Rome is a dangerous city, my dear Giovanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to carry out this mission without any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.96,EN,,0,0,0,,Yes. For the safety of Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.66,EN,,0,0,0,,And the honour of the Medici.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.04,EN,,0,0,0,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Go and find the pit where these snakes hide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.06,EN,,0,0,0,,And be merciless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.20,EN,,0,0,0,,May the father of understanding be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Has Rodrigo Borgia become a messenger now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.40,EN,,0,0,0,,Not necessary, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.52,EN,,0,0,0,,The death of Duke of Milano changes many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:10.44,EN,,0,0,0,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.00,EN,,0,0,0,,The alliances of men are fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:16.30,EN,,0,0,0,,Even the city can change hands as easily as money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.24,EN,,0,0,0,,As long as God is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:20.52,EN,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:23.44,EN,,0,0,0,,I am told that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.46,EN,,0,0,0,,Lorenzo de Medici does not show much respect to our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:32.74,EN,,0,0,0,,That is true. But you can force them to obey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.91,EN,,0,0,0,,Florence is weak now. We should take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:36.93,EN,,0,0,0,,With your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.84,EN,,0,0,0,,It is not part of my office to consent to the death of anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.68,EN,,0,0,0,,But my concern is the greater good of Republic of Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:49.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Therefore I am ready to offer you my spiritual support.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.66,EN,,0,0,0,,And military help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:58.02,EN,,0,0,0,,To ensure order is maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:04.84,EN,,0,0,0,,Preserve the honor of the Holy Seal, Rodrigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:08.12,EN,,0,0,0,,You can count on me, Your Holiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.90,0:25:38.20,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for the man who just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:40.98,EN,,0,0,0,,You must have seen him. Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:44.94,EN,,0,0,0,,It has been very quiet here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.78,EN,,0,0,0,,I have seen no other man besides you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.78,0:25:52.50,EN,,0,0,0,,A hood covers his face. He wore black clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:56.16,EN,,0,0,0,,I cannot help you. Maybe God can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:25:57.62,EN,,0,0,0,,Pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:00.78,EN,,0,0,0,,You will find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.58,0:26:27.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Your blade won't be enough, assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:35.24,EN,,0,0,0,,What happens now is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.94,EN,,0,0,0,,You have a unique set of skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.54,0:26:42.96,EN,,0,0,0,,Giovanni. That's your name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.14,0:26:48.02,EN,,0,0,0,,A set of skills, I'd be delighted to have on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.12,0:26:53.84,EN,,0,0,0,,And what side is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:59.96,EN,,0,0,0,,The side that is gonna win the war you don't even know it has begun yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:04.08,EN,,0,0,0,,The world is changing under your feet, Giovanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:08.12,EN,,0,0,0,,Join us, and you may live to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.52,0:27:13.46,EN,,0,0,0,,Borgia. Yes, I know your name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:16.44,EN,,0,0,0,,I also know how this is going to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:21.74,EN,,0,0,0,,With your fantasy in ruins and an assassin's blade in your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:27.60,EN,,0,0,0,,We shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.06,0:27:32.20,EN,,0,0,0,,He's all yours. Get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:27:58.24,EN,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.14,0:29:20.36,EN,,0,0,0,,That blade almost pierced your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:31.36,EN,,0,0,0,,You haven't spoken a word since you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:39.78,EN,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Giovanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.48,0:29:45.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.64,0:29:50.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Sforza's assassination was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.18,0:29:54.48,EN,,0,0,0,,This is a fast conspiracy, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.00,0:29:58.36,EN,,0,0,0,,And I'm pretty sure the next step will occur here, in Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.66,0:30:00.84,EN,,0,0,0,,Madonna mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.06,0:30:03.32,EN,,0,0,0,,In concern for the Medicis' safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:05.52,EN,,0,0,0,,For the allies faith and for all...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.28,0:30:08.08,EN,,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.84,0:30:12.02,EN,,0,0,0,,Papa. Father Maffei is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:14.30,EN,,0,0,0,,He wants you to come with him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.46,0:30:17.80,EN,,0,0,0,,He's not alone. Armed men are with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:18.96,EN,,0,0,0,,Calmati, figlio.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:25.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Why would Lorenzo de Medici would send guards for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.18,0:30:26.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:30.92,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:47.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Go back and tell Maffei I'm already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Buy me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.88,0:30:51.54,EN,,0,0,0,,Federico. I'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.04,0:30:53.16,EN,,0,0,0,,You're the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:55.46,EN,,0,0,0,,Protect the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:57.72,EN,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.44,0:31:33.85,EN,,0,0,0,,I told you my father isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:44.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.04,0:31:52.70,EN,,0,0,0,,And don't ever doubt the word of Auditore again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:55.92,EN,,0,0,0,,Leave this place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.64,0:32:27.84,EN,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.80,0:32:31.06,EN,,0,0,0,,Our main problem is that damned assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:34.20,EN,,0,0,0,,And the investigation threatens our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.20,0:32:37.82,EN,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll deal with Giovanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:41.54,EN,,0,0,0,,I've already got something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.20,0:32:47.52,EN,,0,0,0,,And then, nothing will stand in our way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:18.40,EN,,0,0,0,,My dear sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.10,0:33:22.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Dark skies are rising over Florence and time is running low.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.22,0:33:25.44,EN,,0,0,0,,The enemy is closer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.06,0:33:29.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Now, the final battle is about to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.78,0:33:34.34,EN,,0,0,0,,Every man is mortal and every life comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.46,0:33:36.68,EN,,0,0,0,,But certain things will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.10,0:33:40.04,EN,,0,0,0,,Federico and Ezio, my sons...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.04,0:33:43.86,EN,,0,0,0,,Always remember,we are Auditori di Firenze
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:46.32,EN,,0,0,0,,And we are assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.66,CN,,0,0,0,,1476年  意大利迎来了新时代的破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:17.96,CN,,0,0,0,,艺术  文化和科学在各种灵感的引导下迅速发展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:32.02,CN,,0,0,0,,文艺复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.26,CN,,0,0,0,,这也许就是历史记录我们的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:45.06,CN,,0,0,0,,不过  在金钱和知识的阴影下  隐藏着另一个真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:50.02,CN,,0,0,0,,腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:51.58,CN,,0,0,0,,背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.74,CN,,0,0,0,,谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.62,CN,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:00:59.38,CN,,0,0,0,,秘密很危险  我必须将其隐藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:01.10,CN,,0,0,0,,即使是我家人  也不能告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.40,CN,,0,0,0,,家庭  正义  荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.80,CN,,0,0,0,,它们都是引导我刀刃的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:15.90,CN,,0,0,0,,真相以血写成  我会在阴影笼罩之下发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.28,CN,,0,0,0,,我叫乔瓦尼·奥迪托雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.98,CN,,0,0,0,,我和我的先祖们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.16,CN,,0,0,0,,我是一名刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.56,CN,,0,0,0,,你跟我来  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.46,CN,,0,0,0,,我在他们到达佛罗伦萨之前阻止了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.34,CN,,0,0,0,,不幸的是  陛下  第四个人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.44,CN,,0,0,0,,乔瓦尼  你听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.02,CN,,0,0,0,,传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.06,CN,,0,0,0,,是关于一个足以改变权力格局的大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.84,CN,,0,0,0,,你抓到的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.20,CN,,0,0,0,,他开口说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.72,CN,,0,0,0,,他会把他知道的都一五一十地吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.56,CN,,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.20,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:20.98,CN,,0,0,0,,在米兰  圣诞节那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:30.38,CN,,0,0,0,,大弥撒封赐圣斯特法诺的牧师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.35,CN,,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:38.38,CN,,0,0,0,,当唱诗班在祭坛的回声越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:45.96,CN,,0,0,0,,当钟声响起第十二次和最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:52.78,CN,,0,0,0,,在祭坛上的唱诗班的回声越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.50,CN,,0,0,0,,当钟声响起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:04.70,CN,,0,0,0,,第十二次和最后一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.80,CN,,0,0,0,,米兰公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.17,CN,,0,0,0,,将会死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.34,CN,,0,0,0,,停手  快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.46,CN,,0,0,0,,别杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.08,CN,,0,0,0,,亲爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.88,CN,,0,0,0,,艾吉奥学得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.80,CN,,0,0,0,,让我想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:37.09,CN,,0,0,0,,艾吉奥  记住  你必须先人一着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:42.80,CN,,0,0,0,,别等你的对手出手  要抢占先机  然后出其不意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.48,CN,,0,0,0,,父亲  你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.54,CN,,0,0,0,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:04.18,CN,,0,0,0,,米兰公爵的死  让洛伦佐·德·美第奇失去了一个强大的盟友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.44,CN,,0,0,0,,我很肯定他的敌人已经策划了下一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.22,CN,,0,0,0,,斯福尔扎之死不是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:17.36,CN,,0,0,0,,而是开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:22.04,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道应该在哪里继续我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.76,CN,,0,0,0,,你过去对我们非常尽责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.06,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我们才委托你把这封信交给我们的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.72,CN,,0,0,0,,完美  简直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.66,CN,,0,0,0,,这么多年  我们的时代终于要来了  表哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.58,CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:57.04,CN,,0,0,0,,在这封信成功寄出去之前  你必须以性命来保护这封信  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.56,CN,,0,0,0,,去圣安佐诺大学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:09.38,CN,,0,0,0,,在一家批发商旁边有一座雕像  有人在那里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:11.38,CN,,0,0,0,,不许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.36,CN,,0,0,0,,你主人到底在策划什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.00,CN,,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.76,CN,,0,0,0,,上帝作证  我会割断你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:51.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我的生命不属于你  我的秘密将随我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.78,CN,,0,0,0,,我们地狱再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:16.10,CN,,0,0,0,,乔瓦尼  在威尼斯有什么发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.96,CN,,0,0,0,,我截取到这封密函
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.82,CN,,0,0,0,,陛下  请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.50,CN,,0,0,0,,这封密函有巴巴里戈的印章
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.66,CN,,0,0,0,,我从不相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.94,CN,,0,0,0,,密码
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.08,CN,,0,0,0,,一封被加密的密函
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:55.46,CN,,0,0,0,,这需要几个小时来解密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.32,CN,,0,0,0,,当解密完成了  我会寄给你  乔瓦尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.00,CN,,0,0,0,,去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.78,CN,,0,0,0,,马菲神父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:36.58,CN,,0,0,0,,你成功解密了  非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.66,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道你不会令我失望  马菲神父
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.74,CN,,0,0,0,,去通知乔瓦尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.56,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉他  他要外出一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.66,CN,,0,0,0,,我要等洛伦佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.32,CN,,0,0,0,,神父…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.52,CN,,0,0,0,,记住  你必须保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.34,CN,,0,0,0,,秘密在这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.48,CN,,0,0,0,,也必须在这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.48,CN,,0,0,0,,没有人知道这封密函的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.22,CN,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.28,CN,,0,0,0,,很好  你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.66,CN,,0,0,0,,早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.09,0:18:43.32,CN,,0,0,0,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.74,CN,,0,0,0,,咱儿子在看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.36,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.62,CN,,0,0,0,,你应该和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.14,CN,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:17.02,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉我  父亲  为什么一个银行家总是要在深夜离开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.22,CN,,0,0,0,,生意上的需要  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.74,CN,,0,0,0,,让我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.27,CN,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.34,CN,,0,0,0,,为什么不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.18,CN,,0,0,0,,我需要你帮助你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.40,CN,,0,0,0,,当我不在家里时  照顾好家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.54,CN,,0,0,0,,我想帮助你  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.66,CN,,0,0,0,,你已经帮了我很多了  艾吉奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.93,CN,,0,0,0,,比你想象中还要多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.86,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我们破坏了密函的印章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.10,CN,,0,0,0,,我们必须伪造一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.12,CN,,0,0,0,,埃穆迪神父正在伪造中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.10,CN,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我们无法解密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:15.08,CN,,0,0,0,,只有一个方法能解密这封密函
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.96,CN,,0,0,0,,还有找出策划刺杀斯福尔扎的幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:22.64,CN,,0,0,0,,那就是把信寄出去  它会指引我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:23.98,CN,,0,0,0,,陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:28.92,CN,,0,0,0,,我知道巴巴里戈要把这封信寄去什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.08,CN,,0,0,0,,马菲神父  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:47.86,CN,,0,0,0,,罗马是一个危险的城市  乔瓦尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.74,CN,,0,0,0,,你确定这个任务你不需要任何帮助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.96,CN,,0,0,0,,是的  为了佛罗伦萨的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.66,CN,,0,0,0,,还有为了美第奇的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.04,CN,,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.06,CN,,0,0,0,,去找到毒蛇的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.06,CN,,0,0,0,,无需留情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.20,CN,,0,0,0,,愿洞察之父与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.86,CN,,0,0,0,,罗德里戈·波吉亚如今怎么成送信的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:03.40,CN,,0,0,0,,这并不重要  教皇陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.52,CN,,0,0,0,,米兰公爵之死改变了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:10.44,CN,,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.00,CN,,0,0,0,,他们的联盟不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:16.30,CN,,0,0,0,,城市的统治权甚至可以花钱买来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.24,CN,,0,0,0,,只要上帝在我们这一边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:20.52,CN,,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:23.44,CN,,0,0,0,,我听说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.46,CN,,0,0,0,,洛伦佐·德·美第奇并不想听我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:32.74,CN,,0,0,0,,确实是  但是您可以逼他们遵从您
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:35.91,CN,,0,0,0,,佛罗伦萨现在处于弱势  我们应该从中取利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:36.93,CN,,0,0,0,,若能得到您的帮助…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.84,CN,,0,0,0,,我的职责不是让人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:43.68,CN,,0,0,0,,而是为了佛罗伦萨共和政体的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:49.74,CN,,0,0,0,,因此我可以给予你精神上的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:53.66,CN,,0,0,0,,还有军事上的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:58.02,CN,,0,0,0,,以保证秩序不乱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:04.84,CN,,0,0,0,,保住神圣印章的荣誉  罗德里戈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:08.12,CN,,0,0,0,,您可以相信我  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.90,0:25:38.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我在找刚刚进来的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:40.98,CN,,0,0,0,,你一定见过他  他去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:44.94,CN,,0,0,0,,今天这里很安静
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.78,CN,,0,0,0,,除了你之外  我没见过其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.78,0:25:52.50,CN,,0,0,0,,他穿黑色衣服  有斗篷遮脸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:56.16,CN,,0,0,0,,我帮不了你  也许上帝可以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:25:57.62,CN,,0,0,0,,祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:00.78,CN,,0,0,0,,你会找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.58,0:26:27.50,CN,,0,0,0,,光靠你的刀刃是不够的  刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.36,0:26:35.24,CN,,0,0,0,,接下来会发生什么  取决于你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.94,CN,,0,0,0,,你拥有独特的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.54,0:26:42.96,CN,,0,0,0,,你叫乔瓦尼  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.14,0:26:48.02,CN,,0,0,0,,如果你投靠我这边  我会非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.12,0:26:53.84,CN,,0,0,0,,你是哪一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:59.96,CN,,0,0,0,,我会在你发现战争发生之前取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:04.08,CN,,0,0,0,,你脚下的世界正在发生改变  乔瓦尼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:08.12,CN,,0,0,0,,加入我们吧  你会见证到的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.52,0:27:13.46,CN,,0,0,0,,波吉亚  我也知道你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:16.44,CN,,0,0,0,,我也知道这会如何结束
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:21.74,CN,,0,0,0,,你的幻想将破灭  刺客的刀刃将刺穿你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.36,0:27:27.60,CN,,0,0,0,,走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.06,0:27:32.20,CN,,0,0,0,,将他拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.60,0:27:58.24,CN,,0,0,0,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.14,0:29:20.36,CN,,0,0,0,,那一刀差点刺穿你的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:31.36,CN,,0,0,0,,自从你回来之后  你没说过一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:39.78,CN,,0,0,0,,乔瓦尼  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.48,0:29:45.50,CN,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.64,0:29:50.38,CN,,0,0,0,,刺杀斯福尔扎只是这件事的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.18,0:29:54.48,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一个阴谋  玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.00,0:29:58.36,CN,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定佛罗伦萨会有大事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.66,0:30:00.84,CN,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.06,0:30:03.32,CN,,0,0,0,,为了美第奇家族的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:05.52,CN,,0,0,0,,为了联盟的忠诚  还有这一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.28,0:30:08.08,CN,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.84,0:30:12.02,CN,,0,0,0,,父亲  马菲神父来了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:14.30,CN,,0,0,0,,他要你立刻跟他走
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.46,0:30:17.80,CN,,0,0,0,,他不是一个人来的  还有很多士兵跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.84,0:30:18.96,CN,,0,0,0,,冷静下来  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.20,0:30:25.94,CN,,0,0,0,,为什么洛伦佐·德·美第奇会派守卫找你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.18,0:30:26.98,CN,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:30.92,CN,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:47.20,CN,,0,0,0,,去告诉马菲神父我已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:48.48,CN,,0,0,0,,给我争取一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.88,0:30:51.54,CN,,0,0,0,,费德里科  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.04,0:30:53.16,CN,,0,0,0,,你是长子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:55.46,CN,,0,0,0,,保护你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:57.72,CN,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.44,0:31:33.85,CN,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你了  我父亲不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:44.74,CN,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.04,0:31:52.70,CN,,0,0,0,,以后不要怀疑奥迪托雷家族说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:55.92,CN,,0,0,0,,离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.64,0:32:27.84,CN,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.80,0:32:31.06,CN,,0,0,0,,我们最大的问题是那个该死的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:34.20,CN,,0,0,0,,他调查的东西会威胁到我们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.20,0:32:37.82,CN,,0,0,0,,别担心  我会解决掉乔瓦尼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:41.54,CN,,0,0,0,,我已经有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.20,0:32:47.52,CN,,0,0,0,,这样就没什么能阻碍我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:18.40,CN,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的儿子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.10,0:33:22.74,CN,,0,0,0,,阴影即将笼罩佛罗伦萨  时间已所剩无几
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.22,0:33:25.44,CN,,0,0,0,,敌人比我想象中还要接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.06,0:33:29.34,CN,,0,0,0,,最后一战即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.78,0:33:34.34,CN,,0,0,0,,每个人都将战斗到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.46,0:33:36.68,CN,,0,0,0,,但有些东西是永远不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.10,0:33:40.04,CN,,0,0,0,,费德里科  还有艾吉奥  我的孩子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.04,0:33:43.86,CN,,0,0,0,,永远记住  我们是佛罗伦萨的奥迪托雷家族
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:46.32,CN,,0,0,0,,我们是刺客
